      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PANTHER POTTER (3) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 3.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 21.58. Has a low draw and likes the trip. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Sure to prove hard to beat. EXOTIC RUBY (1) finished third (22.25) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Must be included in calculations. OSCAR TOMMY (2) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when third beaten 7 lengths (22.41). Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Must be included in calculations. HOLLY MAGIC (8) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can turn the form around.",
